name: Carlos H. Conde
text: Do they really know their candidate?    Literally:    Day 1: There are no such accounts  Day 2: OK there are accounts but there's not much money    Day 1: Cut ties with Australia/US  A week later: Who am I to cut ties with Australia/US?    Reputation for anti-corruption --admires Marcos, supported Binay. Now he'll send Binay to jail.    China: enter bilateral talks, give up claim to West Philippine Sea; now he'll go over there and plant a flag. OK.    There is so much more of that.    This is stuff they castigate other candidates for but which they are completely blind to when it's Duterte.    Speaking of what else they're blind to:     https://www.facebook.com/carlosconde.ph/ photos/a.527960643942515.1073741825.136793129725937/943857712352804/?type=3
